<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>WITHER AI - Discord Bot Dashboard</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: #000000;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            max-width: 700px;
            width: 100%;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 3em;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }
        h2 {
            font-size: 1.8em;
            margin: 30px 0 15px 0;
            color: #5865F2;
        }
        .status {
            font-size: 1.5em;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .status-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background: #00ff00;
            color: #000;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-weight: bold;
            animation: pulse 2s infinite;
        }
        @keyframes pulse {
            0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
            50% { opacity: 0.7; }
        }
        .divider {
            border: none;
            height: 1px;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, rgba(255,255,255,0.3), transparent);
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .about-section {
            background: rgba(88, 101, 242, 0.2);
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .about-section p {
            margin: 10px 0;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .about-section .highlight {
            color: #5865F2;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .features {
            margin: 30px 0;
            text-align: left;
            display: inline-block;
        }
        .features li {
            margin: 10px 0;
            font-size: 1.1em;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            margin: 10px 5px;
            background: #5865F2;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }
        .btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            background: #4752C4;
        }
        .btn-secondary {
            background: #2d3136;
        }
        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background: #40444b;
        }
        .buttons-container {
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        .info {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            opacity: 0.8;
        }
        .stats-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .stat-box {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .stat-box .number {
            font-size: 1.8em;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #5865F2;
        }
        .stat-box .label {
            font-size: 0.9em;
            opacity: 0.8;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>WITHER BOT</h1>
        <div class="status">
            <div class="status-badge">ONLINE</div>
        </div>
        <p style="font-size: 1.3em; margin: 20px 0;">Discord Bot Dashboard</p>

        <hr class="divider">

        <h2>About</h2>
        <div class="about-section">
            <p><span class="highlight">WITHER BOT</span> is a powerful, multipurpose Discord bot designed to enhance your server experience.</p>
            <p>Built with <span class="highlight">Discord.js v14</span>, it offers a wide range of features including moderation, economy, leveling, music, giveaways, and much more!</p>
            <p>With an easy-to-use /help, you can customize and manage all bot settings for your server without any issue.</p>
        </div>

        <hr class="divider">

        <h2>Features</h2>
        <div class="features">
            <ul style="list-style: none;">
                <li>Commands - Admin, Fun, Economy & More</li>
                <li>AutoMod - Advanced auto-moderation</li>
                <li>Giveaways - Easy giveaway management</li>
                <li>Economy - Coins, daily rewards & gamble</li>
                <li>Leveling - XP system & leaderboards</li>
                <li>Tickets - Support ticket system</li>
                <li>Music - Play music in voice channels</li>
                <li>Welcome/Leave - Custom greeting messages</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <hr class="divider">

        <div class="buttons-container">
            <a href="/api/login" class="btn">Login with Discord</a>

        <div class="info">
            <p>Bot is running and connected to Discord!</p>
            <p>Click "Manage Server" to configure your servers</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
